{
  "stem": "1400.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "One thing I forgot, and I always say that specially in the schools when I'm talking about the Holocaust for children.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When we were ordered to march from Landsberg camp to the Kaufering camp, which was 5 kilometers or so, it took us most of the day to walk.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "As we walked through the town, townspeople from behind the fences and from the windows threw food between our lines.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this was the first time I-- I-- we realized that they endangered their own safety, because we were marching between the guards, and we were grabbing whatever they threw in.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But they disappeared behind the windows right away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were throwing food, seeing our condition.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German people.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I-- so there was some feeling people, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you have Munchen in one point, Dachau is about 15 kilometers off of Munchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from Dachau down south is Landsberg and Kaufering area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "About 50 or 60 kilometers from Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was, as I said, the last leg of the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By then-- this time it was April, by the time I came out of that barrack.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Barely able to walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And it still didn't end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- I didn't got liberated in, in Kaufering.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Nazis had a-- another saga for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were ordered-- many of the people were ordered and they were marching.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was ordered to go march out to the railroad station and back into the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this time they had open wagons and regular cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But the only difference was that the railroad tracks on one track.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Nazis were retreating with the heavy artillery, ammunition, and all their hardware.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On another track, the concentration camp inmates in the train, train rode.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
